            <title>黑漆版 Leica M11 + Noctilux-M 50 f/1.2 ASPH. 推出，展現經典設計與黑漆機身工藝</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/11/23/leica-m11-noctilux-m-50-f-1-2-asph/dc/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=leica-m11-noctilux-m-50-f-1-2-asph</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/11/23/leica-m11-noctilux-m-50-f-1-2-asph/dc/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sat, 23 Nov 2024 07:00:48 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[數碼相機]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Leica M11]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1276720</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Leica 宣佈推出兩款全新產品：M11 黑漆版相機及 Noctilux-M 50 f/1.2 ASPH. 黑漆版鏡頭。兩款產品的設計展現 Leica 的標誌性風格外，展示 Leica 數十年來獨特的美學理念及精湛工藝。</p><h4></h4><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20230_leica_m11_glos-1-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1276727" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20230_leica_m11_glos-1-694x520.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="520" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20230_leica_m11_glos-1-694x520.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20230_leica_m11_glos-1-scaled.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20230_leica_m11_glos-2-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1276729" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20230_leica_m11_glos-2-694x448.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="448" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20230_leica_m11_glos-2-694x448.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20230_leica_m11_glos-2-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/11731_noctiluxm_1_25-scaled.jpg"><br /></a></p><p>新款 Leica M11 黑漆版採用黃銅材質的頂蓋、撥盤及開關均覆以亮黑色漆面，搭配頂蓋上的「Leica」字樣及亮銀色鍍鉻快門按鈕。快門撥盤及 ISO 撥盤上用上交叉滾花紋理。相機去掉了傳統的紅點標誌，帶來更低調的外觀設計。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20230_leica_m11_glos-3-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1276730" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20230_leica_m11_glos-3-694x448.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="448" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20230_leica_m11_glos-3-694x448.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20230_leica_m11_glos-3-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20230_leica_m11_glos-4-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1276731" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20230_leica_m11_glos-4-694x520.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="520" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20230_leica_m11_glos-4-694x520.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20230_leica_m11_glos-4-scaled.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a>Leica 的 M 系列經典黑漆面自 1962 年首次應用於 Leica M3，深受攝影愛好者熱烈追捧。這種漆面隨時間使用，會逐漸顯露出黃銅色，形成獨特的光澤效果，為每台相機留下專屬於其使用者的故事。</p><h4></h4><p>黑漆版 Noctilux-M 50 f/1.2 ASPH. 鏡頭則專為搭配亮黑漆面的 M 相機而設計。該鏡頭以大光圈及獨特焦外成像效果著稱，並附有圓形遮光罩及亮黑漆面前後鏡頭蓋，紅色「英尺」刻度更增添復古韻味。這款鏡頭重新演繹了 Noctilux 系列的經典特質，為攝影師帶來極佳的畫質表現。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/11731_noctiluxm_1_25-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1276732" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/11731_noctiluxm_1_25-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/11731_noctiluxm_1_25-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/11731_noctiluxm_1_25-1200x900.jpg 1200w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/11731_noctiluxm_1_25-scaled.jpg 1199w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/11731_noctiluxm_1_25-1-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1276734" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/11731_noctiluxm_1_25-1-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/11731_noctiluxm_1_25-1-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/11731_noctiluxm_1_25-1-scaled.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>Leica 同時推出了一系列高級配件，包括沙丘灰色版的可調節背帶、M11 保護套及相機包，均以高品質牛皮製成，進一步完善 M 系統的使用體驗。</p><h4></h4><p>Leica M11 黑漆版的建議零售價為港幣 75,900，而 Noctilux-M 50 f/1.2 ASPH. 黑漆版則為港幣 69,500。兩款產品現已於全球 Leica 專賣店、官方網上渠道及授權經銷商發售。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/11731_noctiluxm_1_25-1-scaled.jpg"><br /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/24040_systemtaschem_-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1276735" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/24040_systemtaschem_-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/24040_systemtaschem_-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/24040_systemtaschem_-1200x900.jpg 1200w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/24040_systemtaschem_-scaled.jpg 1199w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/24041_protector_taup-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1276736" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/24041_protector_taup-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/24041_protector_taup-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/24041_protector_taup-scaled.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/18574_tragriemenm_ta-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1276737" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/18574_tragriemenm_ta-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/18574_tragriemenm_ta-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/18574_tragriemenm_ta-scaled.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><div class="page" title="Page 4"><div class="layoutArea"><div class="column"><p>Leica 香港銅鑼灣旗艦店<br />
地址:銅鑼灣白沙道 12 號地舖<br />
聯絡電話: 2385 0118</p></div></div></div><p>資料來源：Leica</p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/11/23/leica-m11-noctilux-m-50-f-1-2-asph/dc/">黑漆版 Leica M11 + Noctilux-M 50 f/1.2 ASPH. 推出，展現經典設計與黑漆機身工藝</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
